items.name: Blue Christmas
items.description:
The holiday season means different things to different people, and those things change throughout our lives, depending on our circumstances. Society’s call to be “merry” and feel good is often impossible to grasp when we are in our own season of loss, despair or just having trouble because of the many issues facing our world. Blue Christmas is a place to bring all of those feelings. It is an opportunity to acknowledge and accept not feeling joyful, but it is also a time to reflect on what it means to move from darkness into light,to consider Christ’s coming into the world, and to bring light into the dark places of our lives. We hope you will join us as we journey together toward that light.
